  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.aem.dermis.model.AbstractAsset

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAsset, IConstraintAsset, IProperty, ITypeAsset, java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RestProperty, WSProperty
    public class Property
extends ConstraintAsset
implements IProperty
    Represents a property and it's metadata description. Properties reside within a DataModel and can be used as keys for relationships between datamodels.

    Serialized Form
